1b939fca335013","tid":1196323,"uid":132030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T19:06:53.000Z","msg":"要有返啲裝備<br />\n如果大家確定心理面以經真係做好曬心理準備<br />\n要有返啲裝備 倒如頭盔"},{"pid":"55e51652c632fc83321f797381f1044a98639346","tid":1196323,"uid":200062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T19:14:36.000Z","msg":"走出連登做文宣<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1196309\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1196309</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79628375ce8fa2a98206227a9bbe39339f4ab3ba","tid":1196323,"uid":138244,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T19:18:11.000Z","msg":"希望有返啲leader出黎帶住<br />\n有返啲佈處同裝備<br />\n仲要有多啲人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa97592eaf0cc5603e36f8814a0755e7ccfd8b5c","tid":1196323,"uid":53369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79628375ce8fa2a98206227a9bbe39339f4ab3ba","tid":1196323,"uid":138244,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T19:18:11.000Z","msg":"希望有返啲leader出黎帶住<br />\n有返啲佈處同裝備<br />\n仲要有多啲人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T19:19:59.000Z","msg":"現場其實好難有完善既指揮系統<br />\n都係靠自己執生多<br />\n所謂leader只係帶領行動果一下"},{"pid":"d338f17ea4efb78f6d0d39c742293ed33f60592c","tid":1196323,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T19:21:47.000Z","msg":"Yoga fire啦 仲客氣"},{"pid":"bfda78d118c2b8489a60d0666b19a0fc04b6e096","tid":1196323,"uid":154486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fa97592eaf0cc5603e36f8814a0755e7ccfd8b5c","tid":1196323,"uid":53369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79628375ce8fa2a98206227a9bbe39339f4ab3ba","tid":1196323,"uid":138244,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T19:18:11.000Z","msg":"希望有返啲leade